rows.label: qst202007_0010
rows.name: We're back again!

rows.label: qst202007_0020
rows.name: Mmgh?! *cough*

rows.label: qst202007_0030
rows.name: Just waltz in unannounced, why don't you!

rows.label: qst202007_0040
rows.name: Oh, sorry...

rows.label: qst202007_0050
rows.name: It's just that Musubi asked us to fetch some firewood...

rows.label: qst202007_0060
rows.name:
Oh she did, did she? Well, good on you kids.
You can leave it over there for now.

rows.label: qst202007_0070
rows.name: Hey, what was that you were up to just now?

rows.label: qst202007_0080
rows.name: Eh? What was what?

rows.label: qst202007_0090
rows.name:
Well, it seemed as if you had swallowed
something in your surprise.

rows.label: qst202007_0100
rows.name: Nothing gets past you lot, does it?

rows.label: qst202007_0110
rows.name:
I happened to be eating an Invidian delicacy.
Choclit, they call it.

rows.label: qst202007_0120
rows.name: Choclit?! Is it tasty?

rows.label: qst202007_0130
rows.name: Oh, you have no idea!

rows.label: qst202007_0140
rows.name:
Creamy sweetness with a note of bitter almonds,
intermingling in perfect harmony.

rows.label: qst202007_0150
rows.name: One bite of the stuff and you'll never go back!

rows.label: qst202007_0160
rows.name:
It sound so tasty, Tora already losing
mouthwater!

rows.label: qst202007_0170
rows.name: Tora want to try it!

rows.label: qst202007_0180
rows.name: Dear oh dear...

rows.label: qst202007_0190
rows.name:
Dofusay, how old are you? Eating choclit in secret
again, like a naughty schoolchild.

rows.label: qst202007_0200
rows.name: Ah... Musubi?! No, it's not what you think!

rows.label: qst202007_0210
rows.name: Haha, I don't think so.

rows.label: qst202007_0220
rows.name:
How many times have I told you?
You mustn't eat it all at once!

rows.label: qst202007_0230
rows.name: Uh, well, you see, the thing is...

rows.label: qst202007_0240
rows.name:
You know, that Musubi's got quite a presence
sometimes, doesn't she?

rows.label: qst202007_0250
rows.name: You can say that again. I'd hate to get on her bad side.

rows.label: qst202007_0260
rows.name:
You can't eat so much of this stuff, or your health is
going to suffer!

rows.label: qst202007_0270
rows.name: I'll take these, thank-you-very-much!

rows.label: qst202007_0280
rows.name: Aww. But... But...

rows.label: qst202007_0290
rows.name:
There's no use looking at me like that.
I'm not falling for your tricks ever again.

rows.label: qst202007_0300
rows.name: Hmph! Spoilsport.

rows.label: qst202007_0310
rows.name:
Now, come on! Don't be like that. Whatever
will our guests think?

rows.label: qst202007_0320
rows.name: Come, everyone. Dinner is served!

rows.label: qst202007_0330
rows.name: ...Are these dumplings?

rows.label: qst202007_0340
rows.name: ...They are indeed dumplings.

rows.label: qst202007_0350
rows.name: Uhh...isn't there anything else?

rows.label: qst202007_0360
rows.name: ...Where is rest of food?

rows.label: qst202007_0370
rows.name: Ha, I'm afraid that's all there is.

rows.label: qst202007_0380
rows.name: So we've been dumped with nothing but dumplings...

rows.label: qst202007_0390
rows.name:
Correct. Just dumplings tonight.
After all, they are my specialty.

rows.label: qst202007_0400
rows.name: You should try them. They're delish, really!

rows.label: qst202007_0410
rows.name: Second-best thing I ever tasted!

rows.label: qst202007_0420
rows.name: Only second-best?

rows.label: qst202007_0430
rows.name: Yeah, first one being choclit, by a mile!

rows.label: qst202007_0440
rows.name:
Oh do give it a rest, Dofusay. It's bad
manners.

rows.label: qst202007_0450
rows.name:
Ah, please, feel free to tuck in.
Help yourselves!

rows.label: qst202007_0460
rows.name: Hrmmm...

rows.label: qst202007_0470
rows.name: This delicious!

rows.label: qst202007_0480
rows.name: Listen to Tora. It's not half bad!

rows.label: qst202007_0490
rows.name: It's seasoned with just enough salt.
